Files.Description: SQL Server 2012 Service Pack 2 (x86 and x64) - DVD (Chinese-Simplified)
Files.Notes:
Recommended SP2 Hotfix available: SQL Server 2012 with Service Pack 2 (Slipstream) ISO/DVD images released on 7/1/2014 were previously disabled to fix an installation issue as described in KB Article 2984316. If you downloaded a SQL Server 2012 with Service Pack 2 slipstream between 7/1/2014 - 7/9/2014 you will need to follow the instructions below or install the SQL Server 2012 with Service Pack 2 (Slipstream) ISO/DVD images released on 7/18/2014 as these images include a fix to the installation issue.

Note: Full edition SQL Server 2012 with Service Pack 2 ISO/DVD images were previously made available for download on 7/1/2014. These downloads have been temporarily disabled while an installation issue where Service Pack 2 was not being installed as part of the slipstream installation process is resolved.
  • This does not affect this Service Pack 2 only ISO download
  • For more information, please see KB Article 2984316
  • If you have already installed, or plan to install, a version of the previously released ISO from this site, you have the following options:
    • Apply this Service Pack 2 patch to the RTM installation.
    • Uninstall, and re-install using this updated SQL Server 2012 with Service Pack 2 ISO/DVD image.

Files.Notes:

This download of Visual Studio Express 2013.3 for Windows Desktop contains the latest updates. These cumulative updates to Visual Studio 2013 include a variety of bug fixes and capability improvements. For more information, see Visual Studio Updates and the Visual Studio Update KB Article.
If you already have Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows Desktop (original release version) and run this download, only Update 3 is installed. If you don't have Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows Desktop and run this download, both Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows Desktop and Update 3 are installed. In either case, Visual Studio 2013 Language Packs (original release versions) can also be installed.

Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows provides the core tools that are required to build compelling, innovative apps for Windows Store and Windows Phone. Windows 8.1 is required to install Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows.
This download of Visual Studio Express 2013.3 for Windows contains the latest updates. These cumulative updates to Visual Studio 2013 include a variety of bug fixes and capability improvements, including tools for Windows Phone 8.1 and 8.0 development. For more information, see Visual Studio Updates and the Visual Studio Update KB Article.
If you already have Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows (original release version) and run this download, only Update 3 is installed. If you don't have Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows and run this download, both Visual Studio Express 2013 for Windows and Update 3 are installed. In either case, Visual Studio 2013 Language Packs (original release versions) can also be installed.
